From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: gregordinary <33880035+gregordinary@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 03:23:47 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] rockchip: rk3576-generic: enable the cache commands

The bring-up console pokes framebuffers and DMA-visible memory from the
prompt; icache/dcache commands make a manual write visible to devices
(mw fills land in the data cache and never reach DRAM without a flush).

Signed-off-by: gregordinary <33880035+gregordinary@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig b/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig
index 251e015a..b0466e3c 100644
--- a/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig
+++ b/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig
@@ -69,3 +69,4 @@ CONFIG_DISPLAY_ROCKCHIP_HDMI_QP=y
 CONFIG_ERRNO_STR=y
 # CONFIG_CMD_CLS is not set
 CONFIG_CMD_SMC=y
+CONFIG_CMD_CACHE=y
